{"tid":2423061,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"一句講嗮，你係以色列人定阿拉伯人","createTime":"2021-02-25T15:59:53.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-25T16:31:17.000Z","uid":370061,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"6c54329721eeef9fede45adbaeec0d2e0719ad9b","tid":2423061,"uid":370061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T15:59:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />阿拉伯人<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />巴勒斯坦阿拉伯人<br />\n<br />\n梗係阿拉伯人啦<br />\n以色列人又<span class=\"red\">冇槍冇炮</span><br />\n仲要獨立後<span class=\"red\">冇食水食物</span><br />\n人地阿拉伯人有差唔多<span class=\"red\">兩億</span><br />\n<span class=\"red\">一人一啖口水都浸死你啦</span><br />\n打？打條毛咩<br />\n反正流浪咗兩千幾年<br />\n依家咪唯有乞求下<span class=\"red\">爭取以色列人自治咪算囉</span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2350405e05aeacca94098b2222499c18390bf80a","tid":2423061,"uid":36383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T16:30:30.000Z","msg":"以乜鳩，係 <span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">猶太人</span></span>"},{"pid":"307e149746281e4f2dc7d96738647d79ea011697","tid":2423061,"uid":370061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2350405e05aeacca94098b2222499c18390bf80a","tid":2423061,"uid":36383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T16:30:30.000Z","msg":"以乜鳩，係 <span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">猶太人</span></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T16:31:17.000Z","msg":"sor<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}